<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink393" corresp="#TNV23poem26">
<l>tuṟantataṟ koṇṭu tuyaraṭac cāa</l>
<l>yaṟampulantu paḻikku maḷaika ṇāṭṭi</l>
<l>yevva neñciṟ kēma māka</l>
<l>vantaṉa ḷōniṉ makaḷē</l>
<l>ventiṟal veḷvēl viṭalaimun tuṟavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O mother with hollow eyes, </l>
<l>tormented by suffering, exhausted,</l>
<l>and bitterly blaming virtue,</l>
<l>because you daughter left you.</l>
<l>Hasn’t she returned</l> 
<l>to become pleasure for your grieving heart, </l>
<l>led by a brave warrior with a shining spear? </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
